div class="t m0 x9 hb yac ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">分？这些事物为什么在你们的理解能力范围内，<span class="_ _4"></span>是可以成立</div><div class="t m0 x9 hb yad ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">的？ </div><div class="t m0 x2f h3 y19f ff11 fs2 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">答<span class="ffb">：<span class="fs3 ls2c">其实我也不算是学者型<span class="ls2d">的法师，更不愿意成为一</span></span></span></div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y1a0 ffb fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">名只是研究理论的学者。<span class="_ _5"></span>因为很多研究佛教的学者，<span class="_ _5"></span>分别念</div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.500000,0.000000,0.000000,1.500000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
